{"tid":1685648,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【氣象】（2019年11月上旬）一股季候風補充會於旬中為廣東帶來稍涼的天氣","createTime":"2019-10-31T16:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T17:51:52.000Z","uid":38255,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"858377ec4f54c02fa8b6573bed2f3ebd90f1b016","tid":1685648,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T16:05:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\"><img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://imgur.com/hBEht4a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FhBEht4a.png&h=4c32fde0&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>氣象討論：2019年11月上旬</ins></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">此帖文討論期：2019年11月1日至10日</span></span></strong><br />\n【註】 氣象討論帖一般逢每月1日、11日及21日發出新帖文。 當新帖文發出後，或有颱風追擊帖發出，原有的氣象討論帖會隨即停用。 為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請關注<span style=\"color: red;\">氣象巴打&bull;高登氣象台</span>最新動態<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/z4brcbr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fz4brcbr.png&h=d512611e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://imgur.com/2v9xh70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F2v9xh70.png&h=7ef830e1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/gnzQsWS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FgnzQsWS.png&h=54316817&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://imgur.com/7sNQ3N2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F7sNQ3N2.png&h=15a63bfa&s={SIZE}\" /></span></em><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>◤溫度術語</ins></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">嚴寒      ≦ 7 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">寒冷      8 - 12 &deg;C</span