//j.mp/2ahInaZ\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2ajChbn\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/2ap2lTE\" /><br />\n▲ 衛星雲圖<br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://x.co/1Oc5V\" /><br />\n<img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/Meu94L\" /> <img data-no-cache src=\"http://j.mp/pSSahs\" /><br />\n▲ 熱帶系統</strong>"},{"pid":"f4fcb1436ee63c40b987b353115ceb80703500e8","tid":1685648,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T16:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/195920_a8eb65cd89e86366b8adbf9ac89d9381.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F195920_a8eb65cd89e86366b8adbf9ac89d9381.png&h=fae8adfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/195923_e99c938c30cd56e0bccaf84c7e4a6b39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F195923_e99c938c30cd56e0bccaf84c7e4a6b39.png&h=60556b31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/195927_6b3db2a3d336e5e387ba5704a51812cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F195927_6b3db2a3d336e5e387ba5704a51812cb.png&h=85440aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/200632_7fe23404e4af61b17fb5eb78279ea69b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F200632_7fe23404e4af61b17fb5eb78279ea69b.png&h=27f79c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGW （gale warning)-由日本氣象廳發出，意思係24小時內會有熱帶風暴形成，即係估計24小時內命名<br />\nTCFA (tropical cyclone formation alert)-由JTWC發出，指24小時會有熱帶氣旋（包括熱帶低氣壓）生成，即24小時內正式編號升格<br />\nFFS-美國全球預報系統(GFS)的俗稱，諷刺其計算結果如同FF，但近一年預報準確度有所提升<br />\nCPA TO HK-該風暴與本港之最接近距離<br />\nJTWC BIN C之旅-收集每報JTWC預報報文中的CPA TO HK，事後可以實際CPA TO HK對照作BIN C之用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n馮瑞權-澳門氣象局前局長<br />\n風水權-馮瑞權俗稱<br />\n風水靜，神婆靜，作法靜，巫婆靜-前任澳門氣象局副局長梁嘉靜俗稱，現為首席顧問高級技術員，一度停職4個月。<br />\n赤的疑惑-高登氣象台台長<br />\n七長官/7長官-製作氣象台警報gif會員<br />\nRose-製作高登風格天氣警告圖的會員，其作品並不授予連登使用<br />\n楊振權副庭長-Baroclinic於高登的最新名字<br />\n桜の抹茶刺身-連登氣象post負責人1<br />\n道地檸檬綠茶-連登氣象post負責人2<br />\n雪菜肉絲炆米-連登颱風航空交通post負責人<br />\n一個地球人-連登中仔細分析颱風走向及其他高空氣象圖的高質會員<br />\n當榴蓮遇上芒果-連登中另一位氣象知識豐富的高質會員<br />\n<strong>逝去的不回來/夏天冬天夏天-知名氣溫體感假膠，有去埋其他台派膠既attention seeker</strong><br />\n李棟旭-連登中製作大量有趣的氣象post相關改圖的會員（包括以上四幅術語圖）<br />\n南珠隻狗-連登中氣象知識亦較豐富的會員<br />\n伊甸園菜肉餃-伊甸園市長在連登的最新名字<br />\nXXXXXX堅豎-土豆在連登的分身<br />\n力場J-貼出李首富照片並提醒各巴絲記得準時返工的會員<br />\nDH-direct hit 本港一百公里內掠過<br />\n中出-風暴中心直接橫過本港<br />\n貓5- cat5 五級颱風的英文簡稱<br />\n五隻貓-同上，有cat1-5<br />\n醉警-酷熱天氣警告誤字<br />\n南海之王-氣象迷對香港天文台的尊稱，指其對南海熱帶氣旋預測表現良好，但只限接近廣東沿岸的南海部份，因此又被稱為南海北部之王<br />\nSTNR-滯留不動<br />\nN0.1-向北移0.1度，/E/S/W（東/南/西）同理<br />\n8中X-天文台指定8個測風站中有X個達標<br />\nlogin-登陸，源於cctvb錯將&Prime;登陸&Prime;打成&Prime;登錄&Prime;<br />\nlogin password-由上引申之術語，意指登陸地<br />\n近岸爆發-熱帶氣旋在靠近沿岸時急劇增強，令沿岸地區威脅大增<br />\n0號觀望訊號-香港傳媒於熱帶氣旋仍末形成時，已大肆吹奏香港會打風；又或熱帶氣旋已形成，但並非採取接近本港之路徑，傳媒卻仍吹奏有機會打風。此詞用於諷刺傳媒猶如代替天文台發出熱帶氣旋警告訊號<br />\n(香港)暴雨走廊-指大嶼山東北起，經荃青葵，擴展至沙田大埔一段，因西南水汽易受此一帶地型抬升影響較易有暴雨。靈感來自美國「龍捲風走廊」。以下為經典例子。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/05/153524_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F05%2F153524_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=33884fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/223536_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F223536_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e80d38ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖為一分鐘風速標準，轉化至十分鐘標準（hko,jma標準）請乘0.93<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nchan ho.jpg-副檔名可以改為任意三個不同英文字，為伊甸園市長愛用圖片，即下圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/223635_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F223635_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c1ebcd9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下圖為兩登氣象台提及峴港時愛用cap圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/11/223706_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F11%2F223706_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5d8a07b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa60a535c335b52cfbff312d489793453874241c","tid":1685648,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:13:36.000Z","msg":"green tea sashimi<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0032b9472f5a5f4b67c3bfe764b9a168d853ecf","tid":1685648,"uid":41423,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T23:29:43.000Z","msg":"繼續轉涼吧！香港！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742a202c2ab04792dd2deeeedc985d54c1bd2eae","tid":1685648,"uid":162037,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:22:08.000Z","msg":"好凍，完全唔似20度"},{"pid":"eaeca5af2d14cd0335a2237d3d4d9a1b84fc499e","tid":1685648,"uid":318276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T19:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90517bb26a00bc160b5b51247ab4790d5e68a1ee","tid":1685648,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgur.com/Pskei0w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FPskei0w.png&h=13bd482a&s={SIZE}\" /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">颱風追擊</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>此帖文已停用，請在以下帖文集中討論：</ins></span></span><br />\n【颱風追擊】